{"tid":1198916,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【必玩】示威模擬器 RIOT - Civil Unrest","createTime":"2019-06-10T11:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T01:31:49.000Z","uid":28366,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"047ad8e15556896a4437aab8638ddb2b8ab189b9","tid":1198916,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:00:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steamcommunity/public/images/clans/8557065/a1333bf65a81a7aba326db2a33e8ffd48f1c3044.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsteamcdn-a.akamaihd.net%2Fsteamcommunity%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fclans%2F8557065%2Fa1333bf65a81a7aba326db2a33e8ffd48f1c3044.gif&h=90fe1e67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aDVG74B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaDVG74B.gif&h=eef59e7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://octocurio.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/tumblr_nnolwh2prM1u4rawro4_1280.gif?x86451\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Foctocurio.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F05%2Ftumblr_nnolwh2prM1u4rawro4_1280.gif%3Fx86451&h=fbaff601&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/AngelicClearBrontosaurus-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FAngelicClearBrontosaurus-size_restricted.gif&h=a6481515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《RIOT》是一個暴亂模擬器，按照時間跟地點的流程一個一個的過發生在全球的暴亂事件，一方扮演警察一方<span style=\"color: red;\">扮演暴徒</span>進行對抗。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>遊戲內容：</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">扮演暴民</span>：<br />\n1、指揮領導者、暴徒（武裝和非武裝）、鼓動者和記者<br />\n2、煽動憤怒，使群眾採取積極行動或通過戰術讓人群突進和撤退來應對局勢<br />\n3、使用雞尾酒，煙花，紙炸彈，岩石，街道設施和媒體的力量來攻擊警察</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://blob.steamcn.com/forum/201903/06/112512zn3u5q0qi86f7fc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fblob.steamcn.com%2Fforum%2F201903%2F06%2F112512zn3u5q0qi86f7fc5.jpg&h=069b41fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/app/342310/RIOT_Civil_Unrest/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F342310%2FRIOT_Civil_Unrest%2F&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCBT9vY2lxR77dvs0GIZdErU%3D&h=e03804ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/app/342310/RIOT_Civil_Unrest/</a>"},{"pid":"eb1816bfed0ccd0a925fef58de15e5f95c9d9884","tid":1198916,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:00:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed3390b6cf52056e4fb2a674ebe6c9960e1c02e0","tid":1198916,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:03:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32c7152f3902fbe49eef874352e8ad6ea7d6871c","tid":1198916,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:04:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a038b91a90cbfa713b8d8c45931dee3fe422479","tid":1198916,"uid":79563,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:04:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19aaad5b48be1611f436deca611b4cbf361f3d36","tid":1198916,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a038b91a90cbfa713b8d8c45931dee3fe422479","tid":1198916,"uid":79563,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:04:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:04:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93dd4c508af355255cc5d993bc3b62ec6101bc7","tid":1198916,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7a038b91a90cbfa713b8d8c45931dee3fe422479","tid":1198916,"uid":79563,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:04:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T11:05:18.000Z","msg":"想阻止小麗就係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1741ead4519d5cbbe1c4683da